originalSql:
SELECT 
    a.name AS actor_name, 
    t.title AS movie_title, 
    t.production_year, 
    STRING_AGG(DISTINCT kw.keyword, ', ') AS keywords, 
    c.kind AS cast_type, 
    cn.name AS company_name
FROM 
    cast_info ci
JOIN 
    aka_name a ON ci.person_id = a.person_id
JOIN 
    aka_title t ON ci.movie_id = t.movie_id
JOIN 
    movie_companies mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id
JOIN 
    company_name cn ON mc.company_id = cn.id
JOIN 
    comp_cast_type c ON ci.person_role_id = c.id
JOIN 
    movie_keyword mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id
JOIN 
    keyword kw ON mk.keyword_id = kw.id
WHERE 
    t.production_year > 2000
    AND c.kind IN ('Actor', 'Producer')
GROUP BY 
    a.name, t.title, t.production_year, c.kind, cn.name
ORDER BY 
    t.production_year DESC, a.name

SELECT COALESCE(MIN("s1"."name"), MIN("s1"."name")) AS "ACTOR_NAME", MIN("aka_title"."title") AS "MOVIE_TITLE", "aka_title"."production_year" AS "PRODUCTION_YEAR", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "keyword"."keyword", ', ') AS "KEYWORDS", MIN("comp_cast_type"."kind") AS "CAST_TYPE", MIN("company_name"."name") AS "COMPANY_NAME", "s1"."name"
FROM "cast_info"
INNER JOIN "s1" ON "cast_info"."person_id" = "s1"."person_id"
INNER JOIN "aka_title" ON "cast_info"."movie_id" = "aka_title"."movie_id"
INNER JOIN "movie_companies" ON "aka_title"."id" = "movie_companies"."movie_id"
INNER JOIN "company_name" ON "movie_companies"."company_id" = "company_name"."id"
INNER JOIN "comp_cast_type" ON "cast_info"."person_role_id" = "comp_cast_type"."id"
INNER JOIN "movie_keyword" ON "aka_title"."id" = "movie_keyword"."movie_id"
INNER JOIN "keyword" ON "movie_keyword"."keyword_id" = "keyword"."id"
WHERE "aka_title"."production_year" > 2000 AND ("comp_cast_type"."kind" = 'Actor' OR "comp_cast_type"."kind" = 'Producer')
GROUP BY "s1"."name", "aka_title"."title", "aka_title"."production_year", "comp_cast_type"."kind", "company_name"."name"
ORDER BY "aka_title"."production_year" DESC NULLS FIRST, "s1"."name"
